message: Let's start fair, I'll take the lion's share, but you still get a nice chunk.  What do you say?
Your turn Alice. I'm feeling generous, but let's make it snappy. Time is money!
I'm not a fan of your time-is-money attitude, but I'm willing to compromise. This time, it's 60/40, take it or leave it.
Okay Alice, let's be realistic. 55/45 reflects the time pressure.  Tick-tock!
